thread.title: Houston homebuilders diversify product line to expand market share

title: Houston homebuilders diversify product line to expand market share
text:
Published By: Houston Business Journal - Today 
Homebuilders are offering a wider range of home types, sizes and prices as competition for land and homebuyers heats up in Houston.
